RoutingInfo.AdditionalInformation: TELUS, Bell and SASKTEL jointly operate a common RAN based on MOCN as defined in 3GPP TS 23.251. OTA Steering - Populate 302 220(TELUS), 302 610 (Bell) , 302 780 (SASKTEL) & 302 880 (Common PLMN). Non-MOCN capable devices can only register on the common PLMN(302 880). SS7 Steering - Allow all Bell, TELUS & SaskTel GT addresses & CC NDC found in the respective IR21s. TAP records on Bell core will be produced using Bell TADIG (CANBM).
